Merge data frames

Source: R/read.R
cbind_df.Rd

Merge data frames

cbind_df(list_df)

Arguments

list_df

A list of multiple data frames with the same observations in the same order.

Value

One merged data frame.

Examples

cbind_df(list(iris, iris))
